{"tid":1657065,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[資訊型文宣] 其實有冇必要整個香港政治懶人包比外國人","createTime":"2019-10-16T01:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T03:23:15.000Z","uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73fb776630cf2eef8a5bcb5378bb5b072bf20db9","tid":1657065,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"共產黨（中國人）不嬲鍾意玩魚目混珠。<br />\n<br />\n香港既政制，外人睇落去可能冇咩問題，部分大陸仔仲話香港有民主（所以衰落），有so-called獨立司法/ 有區議會/ 立法會/ 有選舉特首/ 有基本法等等/有好多好多大企業。<br />\n<br />\n但係就係金玉其外敗絮其中，所有係香港社會有大影響力既組織，十中有九都比中共收編統戰滲透控制。<br />\n<br />\n而最近就有人話其實不少鬼佬都需要睇返多Ｄ和平既抗爭云云，有人就指出，佢地生於一個民主既社會，佢地睇到香港，可能問：點解香港人係依個貌似民主既社會仲有咁多武力既抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是垃圾傀儡政府最鍾意玩同一樣野中英文兩個意思／英文寫得好好睇，好似個垃圾監警會咁，Independent Police Complaints Council，鬼佬睇到，喂，independent喎，佢地就可能R哂頭點解香港人投仲訴差佬暴力濫權無門。<br />\n<br />\n我既構想係：文宣整到係好似香港政治101咁，以懶人包方式，比有心深入留意香港既外國人更了解中共手段，區議立會選舉點樣舞弊，分組點票，小圈子選舉等等D仆街野。尤其是中共點樣係慢慢控制商業機構既經濟殖民手段，以地下黨員/ 特務滲透或收買大企業，到最後影響到本土既文化生活習慣同自由，我相信唔少外國人係度都有共嗚。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53133cba25a74c0dd8e9188869a8df489c756077","tid":1657065,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d6da8b18bb2d451bd2e6587753e3ac4f88937658","tid":1657065,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e500d7cd5522f09aa5f876b8a7887855a0d8e648","tid":1657065,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28e9714df92c997e9bcd0f03fc4481487cbbc18a","tid":1657065,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:07:21.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"a314e90b984a23b11a2e986c71d6ac874cb95c97","tid":1657065,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}